<br>
Is that a way to bury the hatchet?  No, that's pretty inflammatory.  Maniak was out of line to ask for the drop, he was imo silly to keep up the conversation, but to go and flame em on a board after he backs off seems "out of line: if you ask me.  But then again this is sposed to be a rant board where there are no lines so anything goes.  That's cool.  Yet Vehnn calling me out of line for pointing out his obvious hypocrisy...well heh that's only more hypocrisy on his part.<br>
<br>
2) Nowhere did I say anything about thinking Maniak was right or that he should have gotten the crap leggings or SMR if it had dropped.  I don't think he should have even asked.  (Course he didn't initiate the conversation, Vehnn did, but that's another story).   My point, which Vehnn has never addressed, is the fact that he is getting upset over being called a liar when it seems pretty obvious to me that he is one.  <br>
<br>
3) I'll summarize again why Vehnn has got to be the biggest moron this side of Bled.  <br>
<br>
Why did Vehnn kill the AM?<br>
To get the SMR. <br>
<br>
Is that cool?<br>
Of course, AM can drop SMR which he "needs" or "wants", there's nothing wrong with him killing the AM to get it.<br>
<br>
So why pretend that he doesn't want the SMR? <br>
No idea at all, maybe he felt guilty, maybe he's just a moron.  He claims in the log to not want the SMR, that he's there powerlevelling a twink or something.  Umm...where's the twink? <br>
<br>
So does that make him an idiot?  <br>
Nope it just makes him a liar.<br>
<br>
So why is he an idiot?<br>
Because he posts a log of him lying then gets all indignant about being called a liar.<br>
<br>
Ok Q&A done.  So what's his gameplan now?  Well when confronted with his hypocrisy he ignores it and sends in the wife to take off some heat with an argument over semantics.  Umm wait though, the wife says he doesn't NEED the SMR in one post but says he does NEED the SMR in another.  Ponder.<br>
